channel.description:
[center]Hey guys, I'm back from a while. I couldnt run a private server on my computer for some java reason. But, i decided to try it again and it worked. So now im back!
Im starting this new server, its like the older ones not 508 crap. I dont really feel like making a list of what i plan to do and what i have done so im just going to post pictures. Its not much but im working on it when i feel like it...
HOME: i still have more things to put on it, but its just a basis for my home. [IMG]http://i34.tinypic.com/fjggef.png[/img]
TRAINING: i will probably put some more stuff in here also... [IMG]http://i33.tinypic.com/14c8jeh.png[/img]
PLEASE COMMENT (NO SHIT).[/center]
